univention-base-files (3.0.1-3) unstable; urgency=low

  * Don't set sshd/banner by default. It might break programs parsing the SSH
    output through expect.
  * Configure the motd through a UCR subfile. This can be disabled by setting
    sshd/motd to false (Bug #31096)

