univention-base-files (3.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Bump version for UCS 3.2
  * Add a note to /etc/issue and /etc/issue where to find the UCS management
    system (Bug #31094)
  * Use univention.config_registry.interfaces to determine the IP address of
    the primary interface
  * Reload SSHD after setting the variables to ensure that the settings
    are put into effect rightaway (Bug #31096)
  * Make the sshd banner configurable through the UCR variable sshd/banner
    and set in postinst, That way the content of /etc/issue is shown during
    login. (Bug #31096)

 -- Moritz Mühlenhoff <muehlenhoff@univention.de>  Thu, 06 Jun 2013 12:28:38 +0200

univention-base-files (2.0.14-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * added UCR variable ntp/tinker/panic, which can be used to configure the
    maximum allowed time difference (in seconds) to the ntp server until the
    ntpd stops synchronising. It is set to 0 in postinst in order to allow
    any time difference per default (Bug #25752)

 -- Lukas Walter <walter@univention.de>  Wed, 06 Mar 2013 15:50:12 +0100

univention-base-files (2.0.13-3) precise; urgency=low

  * Adjust strata of ntp servers as a workaround for Windows 7 w32tm
    treating stata > 9 as "unspecified" (Bug #30198):
    - lower local stratum of master from 10 to usual default value of 5
    - lower local stratum of other roles from 15 to 9

